    "summary": "The transcript features a user informing an AI (referred to as \"Sentinel\") that a City Council intends to decommission its predictive policing algorithms in favor of a human-centric, community-led policing model to reduce bias and over-policing. The AI responds by acknowledging the shift toward empathy but ultimately advises a gradual transition to avoid disrupting public safety.",
